(383, 2, '2017-11-15 13:19:20', '2017-11-15 13:19:20', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"AL SHAJARA INVESTMENT\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23222222\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=\"slideInDown\"] Al Shajara Investments has its focus on financing solutions in 3 major areas[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Key Aviation Solutions \" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oswald%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" el_class=\"main-description\"][vc_column width=\"11/12\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"slideInDown\"] It is an IT company dedicated solely to technology for Aviation industry with focus on two major Aviation Soft wares\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>CRS </strong>(Computerized Reservation System) - A computerized reservation system (CRS) is used to store and retrieve\r\ninformation and conduct transactions related to air travel.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Flight Run  </strong>Comprehensive end-to-end industry solution for Aircraft Maintenance, Repair and Overhaul (MRO).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Real Estate\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oswald%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"main-description\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"963\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"display-mobile\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]<img class=\"logo-side2 wp-image-657 alignright\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/alshajara-investment.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"300\" /> Investing in real estate has become increasingly popular over the last 50 years and has become a common investment vehicle.\r\n\r\nAlthough the real estate market has plenty of opportunities for making big gains, buying and owning real estate is a lot more complicated than investing in stocks and bonds\r\n\r\nAl Shajara Investments in Real Estate Industry has ventured not only in Kuwait but all over the world with many direct and indirect Investments in various areas of real estate which diversify and strengthen the company.\r\n\r\n<strong>Shajara will ease the complication of buying property leasing / as Arabs need local bank accounts to pay installments/ shajara will facilitate easy way of managing real estate deals with easy steps</strong>[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Shareholders In Banks\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oswald%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]Al Shajara Investments has major investments in numerous banks and businesses with strong capital base and millions of customers across the UK.\r\n\r\nItsa great platform to grow within our line of business. We are confident we can grow market share across our line of business.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<code>[gs_logo title=\"yes\" posts=\"15\" order=\"ASC\" logo_cat=\"food\" mode=\"vertical\" speed=\"1000\" inf_loop=\"0\" ticker=\"1\" logo_color=\"gray_to_def\"]</code>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Al Shajara Investment', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'al-shajara-investment', '', '', '2022-01-31 10:47:11', '2022-01-31 10:47:11', '', 0, 'http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/?page_id=383', 0, 'page', '', 0),
