(841, 2, '2017-12-19 13:03:20', '2017-12-19 13:03:20', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"DUNLOP TIRES\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"logo-side wp-image-916 size-medium alignright\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dunlop-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"300\" />\r\n\r\nDunlop is one of the worlds foremost manufacturers of high-performance tires. Dunlop is a brand owned by The Goodyear Tire &amp; Rubber Company, headquartered in Akron, Ohio, which employs approximately 73,000 people in 22 countries and produces nearly 200 million tires each year.\r\n\r\nDunlops history (now approaching 125 years) traces back to the first pneumatic tire and the dawn of motor racing. That heritage is reflected in the design of every tire we make. There focus on performance has led to numerous innovations and breakthrough technologies.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">Dunlop Tires are designed to meet or exceed the stringent performance and safety standards of the worlds most demanding international certification bodies.</div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">Al Shajara is the sole distributor agent for Dunlop Tires in Iran and Kuwait</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Dunlop Tires', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'dunlop-tires', '', '', '2017-12-21 13:36:23', '2017-12-21 13:36:23', '', 0, 'http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/?page_id=841', 0, 'page', '', 0),
