(1022, 2, '2022-01-29 07:32:32', '2022-01-29 07:32:32', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"AFTO\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23222222\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]Amerisolar, Worldwide Energy and Manufacturing Group USA, is a professional solar PV module manufacturer and a renewable energy supplier with 30-year experience in production and quality control since 1993. Amerisolar is also a provider of PV technical services for solar power plant (on-grid and off-grid), including technical design, installation and maintenance, for customers all over the world.\r\n\r\nIn August 2013, Amerisolar adjusted its strategy and started to cooperate with the top-level factories in Taiwan, South Korea and USA to produce Amerisolar modules. With the best and most advanced production equipment in different countries, Amerisolar has more and more competitive strength in US and EU markets with solar modules made in USA and out of China. In 2019, Amerisolar started technical research and production of Energy Storage System (ESS), it\'s first ESS product type is Wolfram-5000.\r\n\r\nIn January 2022, Worldwide Energy Group innovate its business structures and established 6 new divisions: Amerisolar USA (www.amerisolar-usa.com), Amerisolar EU (www.amerisolar-eu.com), Amerisolar AP (Asia Pacific) (www.amerisolar-ap.com), Technical R&amp;D Division, Intelligent Manufacturing Division and Administration Division. In 2022, Amerisolar solar module supply capacity will reach around 9GW.\r\n\r\nBased on the technical cooperation with German and US Institutes, Amerisolar modules have been certified by ETL, UL, TUV, KTL, JET, JPEC, MCS, CEC, CGC, CQC, ISO9001, ISO14001, OHSAS18001 and China Golden Sun. Amerisolar PV modules have been classified in three levels: Platinum Level, Gold Level and Silver Level, which respectively represent solar modules with only plus tolerance, plus and minus 5% tolerance, and only minus 5-8% tolerance, to satisfy different demands from different customers and countries. Amerisolar modules have been widely used in USA, Germany, UK, France, Australia, Japan, Italy, Netherlands, Canada, South Korea, Greece, Taiwan, Brazil, South Africa and many other countries and regions.\r\n\r\nAmerisolar has an advanced Testing Lab by working together German and US experts and engineers. Amerisolar technical services include technical design, installations and intelligent solar plant maintenance. The projects designed by Amerisolar technical team in many countries are generating solar power and protecting the global environment.\r\n\r\nThe earth we are living on is continuously being polluted, and the natural resources like oil, gas and coal will be used up in the future. Amerisolar team are working hard for the solar technology development, solar modules of higher efficiency and solar power plant integrations. We believe in Innovations create future and we believe Amerisolar will be one of the pioneers of solar technology and loyal protector of our green planet.\r\n\r\nLegal Statement: The content in this website in different languages only apply to the contracted companies to introduce and sell Amerisolar products in different countries, and these companies will be responsible for their legal rights and obligations respectively according to the Contracts.\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'AFTO', '', 'draft', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'afto', '', '', '2022-01-29 14:05:01', '2022-01-29 14:05:01', '', 0, 'http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/?page_id=1022', 0, 'page', '', 0),
