(1107, 2, '2022-01-31 10:45:00', '2022-01-31 10:45:00', '[vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"AL SHAJARA INVESTMENT\" font_container=\"tag:h1|text_align:left|color:%23222222\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation=\"slideInDown\"] Al Shajara Investments has its focus on financing solutions in 3 major areas[/vc_column_text][vc_custom_heading text=\"Key Aviation Solutions \" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oswald%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\"][vc_column width=\"11/12\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"slideInDown\"] It is an IT company dedicated solely to technology for Aviation industry with focus on two major Aviation Soft wares\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li><strong>CRS </strong>(Computerized Reservation System) - A computerized reservation system (CRS) is used to store and retrieve\r\ninformation and conduct transactions related to air travel.</li>\r\n 	<li><strong>Flight Run  </strong>Comprehensive end-to-end industry solution for Aircraft Maintenance, Repair and Overhaul (MRO).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Real Estate\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Oswald%3A300%2Cregular%2C700|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"main-description\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"963\" el_class=\"display-mobile\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]<img class=\"logo-side2 wp-image-657 alignright\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/alshajara-investment.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"231\" height=\"300\" /> Investing in real estate h