v class=\"vc_column-inner \">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element wpb_animate_when_almost_visible wpb_slideInDown slideInDown wpb_start_animation animated\">\r\n<div class=\"wpb_wrapper\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-704 alignleft\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/asi-small-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"165\" />Providing aviation services since 1948, Air Services International (ASI) brings a 65 plus year history of providing global aerospace and defense services. ASI provides support for fixed-wing, rotor-wing, and turbine engines\r\n\r\nASI is strategically located with offices at the Dubai World Central (DWC) adjacent to the newly established Al Maktoum International Airport and access to the nearby Jebel Ali Port, the largest container port between Singapore and Rotterdam\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\"></div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Dunlop Tires\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\" css_animation=\"bounceIn\" el_id=\"C4\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"708\" img_size=\"full\" el_class=\"display-mobile\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\" el_class=\"main-description\"]\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-708 alignleft\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/11/dunlop-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"165\" />Dunlop is one of the worlds foremost manufacturers of high-performance tires. Dunlop is a brand owned by The Goodyear Tire &amp; Rubber Company, headquartered in Akron, Ohio, which employs approximately 73,000 people in 22 countries and produces nearly 200 million tires each year.\r\n\r\nDunlops history (now approaching 125 years) traces back to the first pneumatic tire and the dawn of motor racing. That heritage is reflected in the design of every tire we make. There focus on performance has led to numerous innovations and breakthrough technologies.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n\r\nDunlop Tires are designed to meet or exceed the stringent performance and safety standards of the worlds most demanding international certification bodies. Al Shajara is the sole distributor agent for Dunlop Tires in Kuwait\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Flight Run\" font_container=\"tag:h3|text_align:left\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Merriweather%3A300%2C300italic%2Cregular%2Citalic%2C700%2C700italic%2C900%2C900italic|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\" el_id=\"C3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"main-description\"][vc_column][vc_single_image image=\"792\" img_size=\"full\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"top-to-bottom\"]\r\n<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\">\r\n\r\n<img class=\"size-full wp-image-792 alignleft\" src=\"http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/flight-run.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"257\" height=\"165\" />\r\n\r\nFlight run is a comprehensive program to manage airport management system. There are plenty of airport management systems which are dealing with difficulties in managing airport due to capacity constraints, as progressively population is increasing at the airport and management systems are unable to provide services at the right time to the customers which are results as poor services and delays.\r\n\r\nFlight run is a smart airport management system which is designed to enhance and support airport operations from land side to air side and covers all operations from landing to take off. By using Flight run smart system you will have effective control upon all operations.\r\n\r\nFlight run smart airport management system covers allocation of resources and communication process with all channels.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column][vc_column_text]<code>[gs_logo title=\"yes\" posts=\"15\" order=\"ASC\" logo_cat=\"food\" mode=\"vertical\" speed=\"1000\" inf_loop=\"0\" ticker=\"1\" logo_color=\"gray_to_def\"]</code>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Q80 Aviation', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '295-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-01-31 11:14:36', '2022-01-31 11:14:36', '', 295, 'http://ghostwhite-seal-280439.hostingersite.com/2022/01/31/295-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
